28
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:17,679
Tiada orang ajar awak senyum?

29
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,440
Buat macam saya.

30
00:03:19,679 --> 00:03:22,639
Hujung bibir naik macam
emas berbentuk perahu.

31
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,320
Senyum begini paling cantik.

32
00:03:26,679 --> 00:03:28,320
Awak harus banyak berlatih.

33
00:03:29,279 --> 00:03:30,759
Jangan asyik bermain
dengan barang hiasan.

34
