73
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:36,320
Dia gagal cabutnya,
maka dia takkan mati.

74
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,399
Dia akan pulih selepas
berehat untuk beberapa hari.

75
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,640
Mati?

76
00:06:43,359 --> 00:06:44,839
Kenapa boleh jadi begini?

77
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,799
Ini salah saya.

78
00:06:47,119 --> 00:06:48,839
Saya yang cakap bukan-bukan.

79
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,440
Dewa Nasib,

80
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,519
awak harus tolong saya.

81
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,640
Bagaimana kita nak pulihkan Tuan Xue?

82
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:57,200
Ataupun ada ubat yang

83
