87
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:15,440
Awak pun tahu peraturan istana saya.

88
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,920
Jika awak nak pinjam buku
dari bilik pustaka saya,

89
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,799
