Tuan Xue, minum teh.

122
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:24,359
Adakah awak rasa sihat sikit?

123
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,679
Tuan Xue.

124
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,479
Awak tiba-tiba pitam semalam.

125
00:11:31,719 --> 00:11:33,520
Taiyi Zhenren kata, roh awak tercedera.

126
00:11:33,719 --> 00:11:35,359
Kami perlu siasat punca kecederaan awak.

127
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,280
Kalau tak...

128
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,760
Saya tahu apa yang perlu buat.

129
00:11:38,719 --> 00:11:39,760
Awak keluarlah.

130
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:42,039
Ya.

131
00:11:57,359 --> 00:11:58,760
Kenapa awak menangis?

132
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,039
Maafkan saya, Tuan Xue.

133
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,960
Saya yang cakap bukan-bukan

134
00:12:04,239 --> 00:12:06,559
menyebabkan awak cabut benang pipa.

135
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:09,080
Saya tak tahu ia akan
cederakan roh awak.

136
00:12:09,479 --> 00:12:11,880
Saya menyebabkan awak sakit.

137
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:16,479
Awak boleh hukum saya atau marah saya.

138
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:19,479
Awak juga boleh mahu saya
menjadi gadis suruhan awak

139
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:21,919
