saya makan dan menyanyi.

140
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:23,840
Jangan menangis.

141
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,239
Saya buat begini atas kerelaan sendiri.

142
00:12:26,479 --> 00:12:27,840
Takkan saya nak hukum awak?

143
00:12:33,479 --> 00:12:36,440
Kenapa awak layan saya begini baik?

144
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:38,760
Awak masih perlu tanya saya?

145
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:47,039
Takkanlah

146
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:50,479
sebab itu...

147
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:53,799
Sebab...

148
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,719
Sebab, saya sukai awak.

149
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:07,000
Awak benar-benar sukai saya,

150
00:13:07,239 --> 00:13:09,719
bukan hanya nak mengenakan saya?

151
00:13:09,919 --> 00:13:11,919
Saya benar-benar sukai awak selama ini.

152
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,200
Saya bukan bergurau dengan awak.

153
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:20,679
Kenapa awak menangis pula?

154
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,719
Saya marah pada diri sendiri.

155
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:26,039
Saya dungu.

156
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:28,799
Awak layan saya dengan baik selama ini,

157
00:13:29,479 --> 00:13:31,599
tapi saya asyik mencurigai awak

158
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,080
dan tak pedulikan awak.

159
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:36,479
Si Burung Biru yang tak berguna
macam saya

160
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:40,880
hanya layak sukai orang macam awak
dalam angan-angan saya.

161
00:14:05,119 --> 00:14:06,000
Tak boleh.

162
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,039
Kenapa?

163
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:09,719
Saya...

164
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:14,159
Saya menangis hingga mata bengkak,

165
00:14:14,479 --> 00:14:15,679
saya hodoh.

166
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:20,039
Lagipun, saya tak kata saya sukai awak.

167
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:12,851
